'''{{Path|/usr/portage/distfiles}}''' is [[Article description::the default directory [[Portage]] uses to store source code files]]. These are typically in a compressed package format. This directory can be altered by changing the value of the <var>DISTDIR</var> varabile in {{Path|[[:/etc/portage/make.conf|make.conf]]}}.

